# Use Start-Right Skills

Use skill-driven grounding as the default entry point:

1. At session start, apply `start-right-quick` via:
   - `.cursor/commands/jc-start-right-quick.md`, or
   - `.cursor/skills/start-right-quick/SKILL.md`.
2. Use `start-right-thorough` when work is complex, cross-workspace, architectural, security-sensitive, or planning-heavy.
3. Re-apply one of the start-right skills whenever scope changes materially or the user asks to re-ground.

Canonical shared workflow sources:

- `.agent/skills/start-right-quick/shared/start-right.md`
- `.agent/skills/start-right-thorough/shared/start-right-thorough.md`
